    <lb n="1"/>ὑπόμνημα παρ᾽ Ἡρακλεώτου Ζήνωνι Νέστω<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τοῖς ἡιρημένοι</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear>πιτρόποις μου. 

