    <lb n="6"/>τητος εἶναι, καὶ ἄλλο ὑπόμνημα περὶ τοῦ ὀργάνου ἀξιῶν ὑ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ᾶς ἐπ</supplied>ειδὴ Ἱέρων ὡμο-

    <lb n="7"/>λόγει ἔχειν <add place="supralinear">ἐνέχυρον</add> τὸ ἀπολόμενον ὄργαν<add place="supralinear">ον</add> ἔνδοθεν πρὸς δραχμὰς ἑκα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὸν κα</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὶ</unclear> πέντε <num value="105"/> κομισα-

    <lb n="8"/>μένους ἀποδοῦναί μοι αὐτὸ ἢ <supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ἕτερον</supplied> μηθ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὲ</unclear>ν ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κεί</unclear>νου χεῖρον ἀγορά<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σαι καὶ δοῦνα</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ί</unclear> μοι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὅ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">π</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ως</unclear> 

