    <lb n="13"/>θέρωι ἕως τοῦ εἰς ἀγῶνα εἰσελθεῖν· ὑμεῖς δὲ παρέχετέ μοι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εἰς</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρέα</supplied> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἑκάστο</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear> μηνὸς δρα-

